mil.nga.wkb.geom

Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.nga.wkb.geom.Geometry
      • mil.nga.wkb.geom.Point

  • public class Point
extends Geometry
    A single location in space. Each point has an X and Y coordinate. A point MAY optionally also have a Z and/or an M value.

    osbornb
